rComments: This class was really fun! Sometimes dull (like any class), but a great option for a Gen-Ed.
I had a lot of fun with this class.  Some of the material was dull, but it was better than most of my other gen-eds.
Really enjoying the class so far.

Very interesting class if you're into music - goes from gregorian chants to swing and hip-hop. Class is just one big power point (which he puts up before exams) and listening to music. You have to memorize all the music lecture notes to get a good grade. I did, and pulled off an easy A.
A fairly easy intro level class.
